		METHOD method_73208 shouldKeepDraft (Lnet/minecraft/class_338$class_11733;)Z
			COMMENT {@return whether the saved draft should be shown} when opening the chat screen.
			COMMENT
			COMMENT <p>This depends on the method used to open it (represented by {@code this}).
			COMMENT Using the normal chat key, all drafts can still be used. When opening the chat screen
			COMMENT using the command key instead, only a saved command can be retained, not a
			COMMENT chat message.
			ARG 1 draft
				COMMENT the saved draft
